org.openintents.tools.simulator.model.telnet

类 FileThread

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • org.openintents.tools.simulator.model.telnet.FileThread
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class FileThread
extends java.lang.Thread
    FileThread is Thread used to simulate battery events from text file. It's called by FileRunnable, works in background and fires itself when certain time event is reached.
    作者:
    Josip Balic

      • FileThread

        public FileThread(java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> dateTime,
                  java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> simulation,
                  java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> time2,
                  java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> values2,
                  long[] time4,
                  TelnetServer telnetServer,
                  java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.Integer> places)
        Constructor for FileThread. Used to initialize variables.
        参数:
        dateTime - , ArrayList that contains date and time of simulations.
        simulation - , ArrayList that contains type of simulations.
        time2 - , ArrayList that contains time of events.
        values2 - , ArrayList that contains values in certain times.
        time4 - , long[] that contains time of events converted to long milliseconds.
        telnetServer - , TelnetServer through which we send battery values to emulator.
        places - , ArrayList that contains places when second time date is reached.

    • 方法详细资料

      • run

        public void run()
        This method is called when thread runs itself. In this method we use variables previously initialized through constructor. Time events are generated to threads sleep method. Thread is at sleep between time intervals. Once new time interval is reached, thread is called up and battery value is send to emulator.
        指定者:
        run 在接口中 java.lang.Runnable
        覆盖:
        run 在类中 java.lang.Thread
